Description_lang: Mug and Zee take turns being the Head Honcho. Whenever $?diff16[all][the majority of players] players are on either Mug or Zee's side of the room that head takes charge, removing 10 applications of Moxie and granting Mug'Zee a unique set of abilities. In addition, when Mug takes control, he unleashes $@spellname468658. When Zee takes control, he begins his assault with $@spellname468694.
